data.value: ClearnerBot was designed with one goal in mind: Clean, clean, clean! Capable of running around the clock, cleanerbot constantly runs over the floors of your house to clean impurities. Embedded with ultrasonic sensors, it can adapt to new movement patterns without bumping into anything. For a mere $150, you’ll forget what it was ever like to live with dust in your house!
